_sText:
**fy_dustboxnew**

This is a small funmap which is ideal for 1on1 or six players maximum. You start with a desert eagle and knife. In the middle of the map, there is a UMP machine pistol which can be the decisive element over win or lose.

A good movement can bring you big advantages over your opponent! Many spots can be reached with trickjumps more effectifely than with the normal walk-way.
The map contains one nice secret.
